(Note: Demons will decide these. This is just an example.)

	In order of severity, We, (your names here), declare the
	Punishments for the violation of the Rules of the Guild:

  1.	Expulsion from the guild.
  2.	Execution.
  3.	A suicide mission (e.g. "kill Wolfen", "bring me the Lordslayer sword"
	or "conquer the ninja guild").
  4.	Losing the position of an Enforcer.
  5.	Monetary ot material fine, or confiscation of possessions.
  6.	Mandatory work or activity.

	Or any other penalty deemed fit by the Guild leaders.
